  prbplem_type, int, "问题类型\n0：重叠覆盖+MOD3干扰+自定义MOD3干扰；\n1：重叠覆盖+MOD3干扰；\n2：重叠覆盖+自定义MOD3干扰\n3：MOD3干扰+自定义MOD3干扰\n4：重叠覆盖\n5：MOD3干扰\n6：自定义MOD3干扰", A, null, "以mrkey,cellkey分组\n1、满足sum(is_overlap)>0 and sum(is_mod3interfer)>0 and sum(is_mod3interfer_custom)>0则赋值为0\n2、满足sum(is_overlap)>0 and sum(is_mod3interfer)>0则赋值为1；\n3、满足sum(is_overlap)>0 and sum(is_mod3interfer_custom)>0则赋值为2；\n4、满足sum(is_mod3interfer)>0 and sum(is_mod3interfer_custom)>0则赋值为3\n5、满足sum(is_overlap)>0则赋值为4\n6、满足sum(is_mod3interfer)>0则赋值为5\n7、满足sum(is_mod3interfer_custom)>0则赋值为6", null, 算法升级, 维度, 无, 无
